                "invention-title": [
                    "Energy-saving and environment-friendly hydrogen combustion engine and hydrogen conversion method",
                    "一种节约能源环保的燃氢发动机及氢转换方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of hydrogen energy type turbofan engines, and particularly discloses an energy-saving and environment-friendly hydrogen combustion engine which comprises a low-pressure gas compressor, a high-pressure gas compressor, a combustion chamber and a turbine, the low-pressure gas compressor and the high-pressure gas compressor are driven through the turbine, the combustion chamber is connected with the high-pressure gas compressor, and the high-pressure gas compressor is connected with the low-pressure gas compressor. The engine is characterized in that a branch duct is arranged at the position, close to the high-pressure gas compressor, of the gas conveying duct of the low-pressure gas compressor, a hydrogen fuel cell is connected into the branch duct, and a hydrogen heat exchanger is arranged on a hot end component of the engine and used for providing preheated hydrogen for the hydrogen fuel cell of the combustion chamber. According to the hydrogen-fired engine, the problem of carbon emission of the engine is solved, the air inlet condition of the hydrogen fuel cell is improved, a heat dissipation cold source of the cell is provided, the efficiency of the hydrogen fuel cell is improved, the comprehensive heat efficiency of the engine is improved, the working temperature of a turbine is reduced, and thrust output and electric energy output are improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及氢能源式涡扇发动机技术领域，具体公开了一种节约能源环保的燃氢发动机，包括低压气机、高压气机、燃烧室和涡轮，所述低压气机和所述高压气机通过涡轮驱动，所述燃烧室连接高压气机，所述高压气机连接低压气机，所述燃烧室驱动涡轮，其特征在于，所述低压气机靠近高压气机处输气涵道设置有分涵道，所述分涵道内连接有氢燃料电池，所述发动机的热端部件上设置有氢换热器，用于提供预热的氢气给燃烧室氢燃料电池。该燃氢发动机解决了发动机碳排放问题，改善氢燃料电池进气条件，提供电池散热冷源，提升氢燃料电池效率，提升了发动机综合热效率，降低涡轮工作温度，提高推力输出和电能输出。"
                }
            ]
